fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.lib.store.javamail.thunderbird

Class ThunderbirdFolder

  • Object
    • javax.mail.Folder
      • fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.lib.store.javamail.thunderbird.ThunderbirdFolder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable

    public class ThunderbirdFolder
extends javax.mail.Folder
    JavaMail Folder for Thunderbird mbox directory/file structure.

    This is the main class for folder analysis and message slicing.

    Warning:Only for reading and without file locking or new messages management.
